Linn first appeared as a [[census designated place]] as '''San Manuel-Linn''' in the [[2000 U.S. census]].<ref name=2000CensusTX/> The name was changed to '''Linn''' for the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusTX/>

